            "block_label": "figure_title",
            "block_content": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Figure 4. SIMD-aware weight packing for ARM NEON with 128-bit SIMD units. Original weights are reordered and packed to align with the bit width so that the weights can be unpacked into bytes at runtime using AND and shift bitwise operations with a 128-bit mask.</div>\n",
